---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero-section">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1>Dr. August</h1>
                    <p class="role-title">AI 賦能顧問 | 生產力教練 | 暢銷作家</p>
                    <p class="hero-desc">
                        協助企業與個人建立「AI 協作系統」，將科技轉化為真實的生產力與競爭優勢。
                        不只是學習工具，而是重塑你的工作思維。
                    </p>
                    <div class="cta-group">
                        <a href="/services/consulting" class="btn primary-btn">預約顧問諮詢</a>
                        <a href="/blog" class="btn secondary-btn">閱讀觀點文章</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-image">
                    <img src="/profile.png" alt="Dr. August (阿杰博士)" />
                </div>
			</section>

            <section class="features-section">
                <h2>Why Dr. August?</h2>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>實戰經驗</h3>
                        <p>擁有豐富的跨領域實戰經驗，從技術開發到內容行銷，能精準洞察不同職能的痛點。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>系統化思維</h3>
                        <p>獨創「AI 協作系統」導入方法論，不只教工具操作，更建立可複製的作業流程 (SOP)。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>人文關懷</h3>
                        <p>深信科技始終來自於人性，致力於讓 AI 成為增強人類能力的槓桿，而非取代人類的威脅。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
        <style>
            .hero-section {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column-reverse; /* Mobile first: text below image if stacked, but better logic is image on top? Let's do Standard Astro Blog width first */
                align-items: center;
                gap: 2rem;
                margin-bottom: 4rem;
            }
            @media(min-width: 768px) {
                .hero-section {
                    flex-direction: row;
                    align-items: flex-start;
                }
            }
            .hero-content { flex: 1; }
            .hero-image { flex: 1; }
            .hero-image img { border-radius: 0; box-shadow: var(--box-shadow); }
            
            .role-title {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: var(--accent);
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            .hero-desc {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
            .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
            .btn {
                padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
                border: 2px solid var(--accent);
                transition: transform 0.2s;
            }
            .primary-btn { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
            .secondary-btn { background: transparent; color: var(--accent); }
            .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

            .features-section { margin-top: 4rem; }
            .grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
                gap: 2rem;
            }
            .card {
                border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
                padding: 1.5rem;
                background: white;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); /* Straight edge enforced by global.css */
            }
            .card h3 { color: var(--accent-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        </style>
	</body>
</html>
